title: Grateful Dead Live at Knickerbocker Arena on 1995-06-22
description:
Set 1

Touch Of Grey, Walkin' Blues, It Must Have Been The Roses, When I Paint My Masterpiece, So Many Roads, The Music Never Stopped

Set 2

Help On The Way-> Slipknot!-> Franklin's Tower, Samba In The Rain, Estimated Prophet-> Terrapin Station-> Drums-> Silent Way Jam-> Space-> All Along The Watchtower-> Black Peter-> Around & Around, E: I Fought The Law,
